Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道剑心在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.69,0:01:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是不是剑心说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在东京认识的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十一话\N寻找恩师比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心真的在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他前脚走我们后脚就到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.89,0:02:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来绯村在东京还有朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.99,0:02:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道绯村的来历不简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想见他一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先回答我一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.37,0:02:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道\N绯村来京都的目的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.11,0:02:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你就这样\N随便跑去找绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他是很危险的事  你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是想见绯村吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果换成是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.83,0:03:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千里迢迢从东京\N到这来找一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.24,0:03:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为会随便的\N做出不该做的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天涯海角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都会去找你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.12,0:03:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就带你们去找剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.10,0:03:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我绯村住在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问到了 小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带你们去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样子对一介的陶艺家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很不礼貌的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.72,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比古清十郎不是陶艺家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.73,0:04:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没这样了  老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情不好  不想见客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我把小姑娘叫回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是心情不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个老不修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.83,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人叫我拿这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  是谁交给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身材高大声音宏亮的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.29,0:05:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.13,0:05:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该先向你磕头的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操很想见你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想带给阿操麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.14,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盟主只留下这么一个爱孙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.34,0:06:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不愿意  见到她有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.35,0:06:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫够了 你该觉醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.37,0:06:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在需要的是心灵的静养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.31,0:06:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你也是御庭帮的成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你从不了解我的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再最后告诉你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.19,0:06:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你非要\N让御庭屋的面子丢光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.36,0:07:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就先把我给杀了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.43,0:07:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会不惜一切把你击垮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你也到京都来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别装了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.74,0:07:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁一路跟着我来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.27,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天早上才到京都的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.35,0:07:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是今天早上刚到京都的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.28,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.42,0:08:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你道歉就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.79,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不一起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回志志雄的住处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我去我就去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.64,0:08:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要打听绯村的住处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.58,0:08:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以互相交换情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你带我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经十五年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间过得可真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找我比古清十郎有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要改头换姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以陶艺家的身份隐居起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫我不是阿谀奉承的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与其和一些贪官污吏\N同流合污
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.01,0:08:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如做个艺术家\N来得自在一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子  一点都没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别转移话题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底找我有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不说我也知道你在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就明讲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.53,0:09:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十五年前\N你没教我的飞天御剑流精髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望老师能教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.91,0:09:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候就是随便收留了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才造成了今天的你\N现在我怎么能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你今天是有备而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.87,0:10:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比古清十郎是唯一\N贯通飞天御剑流的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.14,0:10:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的武功无人能比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.65,0:10:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然还有剑心不会的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心一定是去\N找比古教他武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么剑心武功就更高强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没人打得过剑心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.27,0:10:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于可以见到剑心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.58,0:10:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了志志雄那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想再重回杀手的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您教我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.63,0:10:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑是凶器  剑术是杀人术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.70,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是改变不了的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.17,0:11:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的理想和现实的危难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.21,0:11:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何者重要  你已想清楚了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十五年前我就错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.09,0:11:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋\N你以为出去能帮助你修行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.10,0:11:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个动乱的时代\N我不能再坐视不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我学飞天御剑流\N就是要保护弱小的老百姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你实现了你的理想了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自大的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.41,0:11:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.61,0:11:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先把我打倒了再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还来真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没辄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.73,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流如果练不好的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会走火入魔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.37,0:12:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道现在最重要的是\N要解救那些可怜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.21,0:12:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脾气和小时候\N一点都没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得你的这个伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.82,0:12:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你十四岁的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑法就超越常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的思想并未\N如你的剑术一样成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你年轻时血气方刚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才留下这个褪不去的伤疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心里还在为\N杀人与不杀人矛盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.77,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么练得成飞天御剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么打得过志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.45,0:13:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算飞天御剑流\N能够解救苦难的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.99,0:13:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但剑是自由是\N是不属于任何权利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不明白这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本没有资格\N学飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.37,0:13:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这里没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村就在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.40,0:13:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种笨蛋\N我根本不该教你武功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.07,0:13:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谁笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操  弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.13,0:14:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.23,0:14:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到今天来了那么多客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心  你去提水来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你提你就去提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不在\N老师还不是自己要提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.85,0:14:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是这么没大没小\N还不快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.86,0:14:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在发什么呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.18,0:15:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易见到面了\N怎么不讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间宝贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人就是剑心的老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.16,0:15:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是飞天御剑术的继承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今年几岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.77,0:15:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四十三岁  怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子像四十三岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心已经二十八岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.68,0:15:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十八岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是练飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才变成这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们来到底有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.46,0:15:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是来找剑心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见面以后呢\N不是要一起回东京吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.97,0:16:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就坦白说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.14,0:16:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过想再见他一面而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.55,0:16:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我的笨徒弟\N还这么有人缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的事\N你好像什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.83,0:16:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你们愿意告诉我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.03,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我教那个木头人\N飞天御剑流的剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.40,0:16:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这晚唯一记得的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要他告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你们告诉我他的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰和弥彦都来京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.08,0:16:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么左之助不久后也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.62,0:17:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和志志雄决斗的事就更困难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗次郎回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  焰灵秘剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这次带来什么好东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带来东日本的十本刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了安慈\N你的修行完成了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝙也  你的伤怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.51,0:17:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夷腕坊你还是老样子\N一点都没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有稀客来访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.33,0:18:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这十年都在全国各地流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮助需要帮助的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.84,0:18:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次回来\N只为专程学习飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.51,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是为了偿还\N那些被你杀死的人命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两者都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.18,0:18:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我无法解救\N那些苦命人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.79,0:18:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脾气还是和以前一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.33,0:18:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就教你\N飞天御剑流最后的精髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.67,0:18:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要打败志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你打不倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.41,0:18:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就枉费我一番苦心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.79,0:19:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来京都  你生气吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一半心在志志雄身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄藏身的地方还不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.12,0:19:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心  你从不愿回头看我一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先说在前头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你学会\N飞天御剑流的最后部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.87,0:20:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不必高兴得太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.50,0:20:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你将会背负\N守护这个时代的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个责任是很重大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个人的幸福\N也掌握在你手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个来京都找你的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.39,0:20:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你牺牲了\N对她将是不幸的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.27,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论你有多强  你都只是个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是神仙或菩萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.47,0:20:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.75,0:20:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么\N一定要这么晚回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.25,0:20:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心要开始练功了\N我们不能打扰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.76,0:20:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经达成见剑心的愿望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不嫌弃\N就到我家来住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.94,0:21:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.24,0:21:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流的精髓\N到底是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最厉害的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最厉害的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.52,0:21:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然想到有件事\N忘了告诉剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.52,0:21:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.63,0:21:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四乃森苍紫\N已经来京都要暗杀剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要让剑心知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.53,0:21:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.90,0:21:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的是真的吗\N苍紫来京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.01,0:21:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  他是御庭帮的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你接近剑心有什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.56,0:21:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是苍紫要你做的\N你是不是来报仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.13,0:22:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫和绯村到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.10,0:22:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭帮的人究竟怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这骗子  别再演戏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个够了没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.24,0:22:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是阿操\N我们怎么会找得到剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.85,0:22:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  你也知道苍紫的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.22,0:22:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.42,0:22:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.52,0:22:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.62,0:22:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.33,0:22:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你  但你要有心理准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.78,0:25:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭帮的帮主四乃森苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.82,0:25:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了替御庭帮的般若四报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.62,0:25:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定要杀剑心灭口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.92,0:25:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以重振御庭帮的雄风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.26,0:25:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄利用苍紫的弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.00,0:25:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉机引诱苍紫入党
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.46,0:25:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两人合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.40,0:25:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会发生什么事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.20,0:25:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请收看下集\N苍紫与志志雄结盟
